{"tid":689890,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果法例規定失物認領，失主要俾返報酬拾到者有冇人贊成？","createTime":"2018-06-04T11:58:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T16:24:59.000Z","uid":4618,"like":31,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b09313c66db103524872becc86b5afc35cddb10b","tid":689890,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T11:58:26.000Z","msg":"最近睇日劇先知，原來根據日本法律，如果失主認領物品，係有義務向拾到者支付物品價值5%至20%嘅報酬。連台灣都會規定要支付最多10%嘅報酬，除非失主係低收入人士。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢個條例幾好<br />\n第一，你唔見嘢人哋幫你執返係麻煩到人，俾返報酬好應份<br />\n第二，大部分香港人都係貪心的小狗，有報酬多個誘因將失物交返出嚟<br />\n第三，依家好多時報酬協商都係私了口同鼻拗，有個原則(法例)同公營機關(黑警)仲裁都係好事"},{"pid":"2bada785fe0c12d8b39a07aba845ff02053b833c","tid":689890,"uid":106468,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:01:14.000Z","msg":"好<br />\n等班仆街唔好以為趺左野係條街有人有義務幫佢送去警局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3639dee6bd79ce3568b2bb2668310096fb980e7","tid":689890,"uid":60219,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/200158_1a31be344221177d1514e1c29e04df74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F200158_1a31be344221177d1514e1c29e04df74.jpg&h=3133054c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"066e5f91f644514ec76ee2a7d05ae92eb2c2c7d9","tid":689890,"uid":36478,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba01aa61d6d8bc118cbb34fa7c806c728e28c9cb","tid":689890,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:09:53.000Z","msg":"一開波就0:3<br />\n有冇人講下負皮原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49277a04ae4fda22463a7f8c1259fea64dfbb394","tid":689890,"uid":60219,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ba01aa61d6d8bc118cbb34fa7c806c728e28c9cb","tid":689890,"uid":4618,"